## Canonical source of truth

The same `skills/` directory is the single source of truth for Claude Code
(`.claude/skills/` → `../skills` symlink), Cursor (this rule), and Codex CLI
(referenced from `AGENTS.md`). Edit skill files only in `skills/` — the other
tools pick up changes automatically.
